Name: Flamingo Go With Gun
About the game: Bloodsucker Army are coming for you. They are brutal and fierce. And you are the pink bird who doesn't tolerate people. Use the gun on your back to chase them away. Before your base collapses and don't forget that you are a bird. Use your wings to avoid enemy bullets. During the anti-aggression You can still get better. Don't forget to find those things to fulfill your abilities. This is a 2D pixel art shooting game where the player has to defend the fortress from the enemy army.
